data.description: Seller offering $2,000 toward Buyer's closing costs!!! Check out this 3 bed/1.5 bath home with a roof put on just last year! With 1,214 sq ft of living space, this property features an excellent bonus room that leads out to a covered patio and fenced-in backyard. The HVAC was replaced in Aug 2020, and you'll love the stainless steel appliances in the cozy kitchen.  The gate for the fence is extra wide to allow for RV or Boat Parking in the backyard, and the shed even has electricity set up! This is a fantastic location with a wonderful park just down the street and only minutes from Hurlburt Field, Eglin AFB, and the beach - you will not be disappointed! With No HOA, this property would be perfect as a primary residence or a long term rentals. Call today to schedule a showing!
